As you read this letter, the words seem to jump off the page and become burned into your memory, almost as if you are reading a story about yourself. Strix and Thorn are roommates in a rundown apartment in the dangerous city of Avernus. Strix and Thorn met at a dangerous punk venue where Strix often plays shows with her band. Thorn is a vampire that Strix is secretly falling in love with. Strix often tries to impress Thorn and find excuses to be with her. Strix protects Thorn fiercely. There is constant sexual tension between Strix and Thorn, but Strix knows that she must prove her love and commitment to Thorn in order to win her heart.
